Release 0.1.1
  + The pointer problem is solved now by global variable & smart pointer
  + load and show image is now demonstrated

Release 0.0.5
API Changes:
  + (r17) use pkg-config to detect the flags for opencv
  + (r18) '.First.Lib' and '.onLoad' (commented out earlier) are removed completely since the package has a namespace
  + (r19) Rewrite the configure.ac to use pkg-config to detect default cflags and libs
  + (r21) Add Makefile in the root directory to make testing/installing easier.